adult_comedy.title: Adult Comedy

255766.title: The Kentucky Fried Movie

Nick Cannon doesn't care what the haters think, and that's what gives him his hilarious edge. Taped at the River Rock Casino in Vancouver, BC.

699110.description: More than recipes get swapped in 1960’s suburbia when modern American housewives host dinner parties that soon become boozy, flirtatious and wild.

702832.title: La Lámpara Del Ladino
702832.description: Un indio vive enamorado de la mujer más hermosa del pueblo. Una noche, por accidente, frota una botella y aparece un genio que le concede tres deseos.

703935.title: Screwed
703935.description: A man watches a porn film to improve his sexual prowess and puts what he learned into action as a way to win the woman of his dreams.

704514.title: Astonishing Tales of Terror: Rocktapussy
704514.description: A group of everyday heroes find the fight of their lives in the deep mines of Northern Ontario where they unwittingly awaken an ancient giant octopus.

707803.title: The Art of Love
707803.description: Aging sex toy influencer Adam and middle-aged product specialist Eva are thrown together into a secret assignment to banish loneliness forever.

707899.title: Dennis & Henry's Post-Divorce Checklist
707899.description: When two friends suffer divorces simultaneously, they follow a list from an old college buddy on how to get back on their feet and into life again.

708084.title: Babysplitters
708084.description: When two couples with mixed feelings about having kids hatch a plan to share one baby, it seems like the perfect compromise until things go wrong.

711406.title: Take Me Home Tonight
711406.description: Four years after graduation, an awkward genius uses his sister's boyfriend's party as the perfect occasion to make his move on his high school crush.

712283.title: Sorority Babes in the Slimeball Bowl-O-Rama 2
712283.description: With the escape of the murderous Imp, it's a fight for survival, and only one mysterious sorority girl holds the answers to the gremlin's riddle.

713082.title: My Sex Doll
713082.description: If he wants to avoid a $50 million debt, an adult virgin afraid of women will be forced to have sex with a robot that has the ability to become human.

714283.title: Mama's Boy
714283.description: The life of an arrogant pseudo-intellectual living at home in Texas with his angelic mom is threatened when she falls in love with a self-help guru.

714476.title: National Lampoon's Senior Trip
714476.description: After being required to write a letter to the President suggesting ways to improve education, a group of high school slackers head off to Washington.

723583.title: Da Block Party
723583.description: On a hot summer day, BJ battles a bitter baby mama and a crooked cop to resume his brother’s legacy of hosting the baddest block party in New Orleans.

723584.title: Da Block Party 2
723584.description: CJ is carrying on the family tradition of hosting the biggest jam of the summer until a crooked cop and a baby mamma come to break up the fun.

723875.title: Fortress of Amerikkka
723875.description: A rebel plans revenge against a corrupt sheriff while a crazed general in the nearby woods leads a secret militia to murder all trespassers.

725276.title: Nips & Palms
725276.description: Tired of his dead-end job and empty love life, struggling artist Jackson goes on a journey through Los Angeles to try to spice things up.

100000188.title: Reform School Girls
100000188.description: A juvenile facility and its sadistic warden usher in a new crop of troubled inmates who aren’t about to take their new living hell lying down.

100000558.title: Buds 2
100000558.description: After the release of notorious drug dealer Karl, two best buds struggle to keep it together as he pursues them to get his money back.

100000580.title: Ali G Indahouse
100000580.description: Ali G, a white gangsta-rapper wannabe, gets hilariously entangled in an evil Chancellor’s plot to overthrow Great Britain’s Prime Minister.

100000703.title: National Lampoon's: Snatched
100000703.description: In this madcap comedy, a nice guy goes into the hospital for surgery and, through a series of mishaps, suffers every man's worst nightmare.

100001503.title: If You Don't Stop It, You'll Go Blind
100001503.description: Comedians act out classic sex jokes in this collection of bawdy, off-color skits.

100001746.title: 10 Rules for Sleeping Around
100001746.description: An engaged couple seeking advice from happily married friends learns the secret to marital longevity is an open relationship dictated by ten rules.

100001771.title: Incoming Freshmen
100001771.description: This sex comedy follows an innocent girl from a small town and her promiscuous roommate, as they adjust to their first year of college.

100001774.title: Invasion of the Girl Snatchers
100001774.description: A criminal couple on the run encounters a UFO cult led by a sorcerer at a remote farm where women’s bodies are implanted with the souls of aliens.

100001848.title: Wild Boys
100001848.description: When her father's last will demands her to undertake a treasure hunt, a reclusive woman ventures into the wild and finds her life changed forever.

100001929.title: The Night Before
100001929.description: A womanizer throws a wild bachelor bash in hopes of opening his engaged pal’s eyes to what he will be missing, but which man will truly see the light?

100002041.title: Virgin Alexander
100002041.description: Facing eviction, a 26-year-old virgin makes a last-ditch effort to save his grandfather’s house from the bank by turning it into a brothel.

100002070.title: Bad Cat
100002070.description: A profane house cat must deal with the arrival of his illegitimate son, an accidental killing, his owner's eviction and more within the course of a day of debauchery and mayhem.

0300008637.title: Mike Tyson Mysteries
0300008637.description: The adult animation classic series featuring the voice talents of Mike Tyson and Norm MacDonald sees the champion boxer taking on weekly mysteries!

02229.title: The Disastrous Life of Saiki K.
02229.description:
Saiki Kusuo is a typical 16-year-old high school student… except he has psychic powers. He’s kept his abilities in check since childhood, but with the temptations of high
school now on his mind, he’s bending the rules—and spoons.

0881.title: The Man Show
0881.description: A prank, talk show aimed at men.

0300009670.title: HouseBroken
0300009670.description: "HouseBroken" is an irreverent animated series following a group of neighborhood animals who help each other navigate the complicated life of being a pet.

0300007291.title: Improv Tonite
0300007291.description: This stand-up comedy series is shot in front of a live audience with each episode hosted by a different well-known celebrity who sets the stage for a half hour of solid laughs. Comedians and hosts include Jerry Seinfeld, David Spade and many more!

01560.title: Bob and Margaret
01560.description: This charming, witty animated series focuses on the ordinary lives of a middle class dentist and his foot doctor wife. Together, they tackle such traumas as being burgled, going on a package holiday and deciding whether or not having a child will ruin their lives. They do all this with a gentle restraint and a keen sense of the absurd. Bob and Margaret provides a whole new way to look - and laugh - at life's ordinary occurrences that we all experience.

0926.title: Dan Vs.
0926.description: Dan thinks the whole world is against him. Maybe it is, and maybe it isn't -- not even his laid-back friend Chris is totally sure. Maybe Dan's just imagining it all. But, like Chris, you can't help going along for the ride when Dan dreams up his wild plots to get even with whoever or whatever he thinks is out to get him.

0300007799.title: Blue Mountain State
0300007799.description: Three new athletes on a top college football team learn the extreme high and low of being among the chosen few who are worshiped and tested on campus.

03393.title: MXC: Most Extreme Elimination Challenge
03393.description: Two teams compete in some of the funniest and most hazardous games ever made for TV in this hilarious spoof of extreme sports competitions.

0300006342.title: Shameless
0300006342.description: In the Gallagher home, chaos is king, as the unconventional family runs through endless scams, affairs, and petty crimes throughout Manchester.

0300009213.title: Trailer Park Boys: The SwearNet Show
0300009213.description: Take three Trailer Park Boys, add one dysfunctional TV network, stir in a bunch of illicit activity and a healthy dose of profanity.

0300005124.title: Whose Line is it Anyway?
0300005124.description: Hilarious improvisations and performances by top-notch comedy guests take center stage in this British version of the classic game show series.

0300008432.title: The Oblongs
0300008432.description: An eccentric family lives downstream from a toxic waste site, and finds that life is always presenting a series of unusual challenges for them.

0300006338.title: Plebs
0300006338.description: The acclaimed British hit comedy series about three young men doing the most to stay employed, relevant, and desired by women in Ancient Rome.

0222.title: Diplomatic Immunity
0222.description: A politically incorrect drama about love, power, manipulation and high jinx.

0300009139.title: Hardy Bucks
0300009139.description: A circle of young men entertain vague ambitions involving quick cash, women, and showbiz in this mockumentary about small-town Irish life.

0300004988.title: Fugget About It
0300004988.description: A former New York mobster joins the Witness Protection Program, which relocates him and his family, who must adjust to life in Saskatchewan, Canada.

0300007896.title: The Freak Brothers
0300007896.description: After smoking a magical strain of weed and falling into a 50-year slumber, the Freak Brothers and their outspoken cat awaken in the 2020s and attempt to adjust to the bizarre rat race of modern times.

0300006337.title: Peep Show
0300006337.description: This acclaimed, brilliant comedy tracks the everyday occurances of a pair of highly dysfunctional, well-meaning London roommates.

0300007634.title: The First Team
0300007634.description: Starring six-time Emmy nominee Will Arnett and Chris Geere, this sharp character comedy follows the off-the-pitch escapades of three Premier League footballers.

054.title: Spaced
054.description: Directionless Daisy Steiner and wired urban surfer Tim Bisley are twenty-somethings who lie about being a married in order to rent a London flat.

03318.title: Idiot TV
03318.description: With cameras everywhere, there's no hiding place for dumb behavior. This reality series showcases outrageous footage of the world's biggest fools.

0300006432.title: Crash Canyon
0300006432.description: A family unused to spending time together gets stuck with each other, when a car crash sends them over a cliff and into a place full of odd neighbors.

0300005225.title: Cromartie High School
0300005225.description: Student Kamiyama gets an education at Cromartie High, a surreal school of hard knocks like none on Earth.

0300007907.title: Brickleberry
0300007907.description: Daniel Tosh stars as the lead voice in this Comedy Central cartoon series about a group of national park rangers who are terrible at their jobs.
